                        <strong>General</strong>
                        <br>If the reporting National Society does not have blood donation facilities, but promotes blood donations, it should count people reached with these promotional activities as part of “People Reached” (irrespective of whether
                        they actually donate blood at some other facility). It will be under People Reached Health
